The paper focuses on improving natural language processing tasks, specifically question answering, by incorporating commonsense knowledge. This suggests that it could fall under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves pre-training functions and leveraging external knowledge bases, which could also relate to information retrieval (cs.IR) and computation and language (cs.CC).
